_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1171690/extras/a884c518998e1ee57ca04d5826625983.poster.avif?t=1768340055\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1171690/extras/a884c518998e1ee57ca04d5826625983.webm?t=1768340055\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1171690/extras/a884c518998e1ee57ca04d5826625983.mp4?t=1768340055\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Stronger Together</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wayfinders are stronger together! Tackling story missions or the latest boss hunt with friends as Wayfinder supports 3 player co-op allowing you to drop in and drop out of your friend's adventures and progress together in your fight against the Gloom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1171690/extras/5909dda84a083735f504c60582018eb8.poster.avif?t=1768340055\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1171690/extras/5909dda84a083735f504c60582018eb8.webm?t=1768340055\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1171690/extras/5909dda84a083735f504c60582018eb8.mp4?t=1768340055\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
